---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TopBanner from '../../components/TopBanner.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import PageHeader from '../../components/PageHeader.astro';
import CTABanner from '../../components/CTABanner.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import heroImage from '../../assets/images/chapters/iceland/iceland-banner.webp';
import WorkingCommittee from '../../components/WorkingCommittee.astro';
---

<Layout title="Iceland - FiNAN">
  <main>
    <TopBanner />
    <Navbar />
    <PageHeader
      title="Iceland"
      description="Explore healthcare opportunities in Iceland, the land of fire and ice, known for its innovative healthcare system and high quality of life."
      backgroundImage={heroImage}
      backgroundAlt="Reykjavik, Iceland"
    />

    <section class="bg-white py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <h2 class="mb-8 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
            Healthcare in Iceland
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-6 text-gray-700">
            Iceland offers unique opportunities for Filipino healthcare
            professionals in a country known for its innovative healthcare
            system, high quality of life, and stunning natural beauty. This
            Nordic island nation combines cutting-edge medical technology with a
            strong emphasis on preventive care and patient satisfaction.
          </p>

          <p class="mb-6 text-gray-700">
            With one of the world's highest life expectancies and lowest infant
            mortality rates, Iceland's healthcare system is a model of
            efficiency and quality. Healthcare professionals enjoy excellent
            working conditions, competitive compensation, and the opportunity to
            work in a system that consistently ranks among the world's best.
          </p>

          <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
            Healthcare Innovation
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-6 text-gray-700">
            Iceland's healthcare system is characterized by its use of advanced
            technology, comprehensive electronic health records, and emphasis on
            research and development. The country's unique genetic database and
            focus on precision medicine provide healthcare professionals with
            opportunities to participate in groundbreaking medical research and
            innovative treatment approaches.
          </p>

          <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
            Land of Fire and Ice
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-6 text-gray-700">
            Living in Iceland means experiencing dramatic landscapes of
            glaciers, volcanoes, geysers, and the Northern Lights. The Icelandic
            culture values creativity, education, and community, creating a
            welcoming environment for international healthcare professionals.
            The country offers excellent work-life balance with access to
            geothermal pools, hiking trails, and cultural activities.
          </p>

          <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
            Professional Excellence
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Healthcare professionals in Iceland benefit from a system that
            prioritizes continuous improvement, evidence-based practice, and
            professional development. The small population allows for close
            collaboration between healthcare teams and the opportunity to make
            meaningful contributions to public health outcomes while enjoying
            one of the world's most beautiful and safe living environments.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <WorkingCommittee country="iceland" />
    <CTABanner />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
